statements: SELECT * FROM influencer_partnerships;
SELECT influencer_name, partner_name, collaboration_type FROM influencer_partnerships WHERE id = 1;
SELECT partner_name FROM influencer_partnerships WHERE collaboration_type = 'Sponsored';
SELECT * FROM influencer_partnerships WHERE collaboration_start_date >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT influencer_name, partner_name FROM influencer_partnerships ORDER BY collaboration_end_date DESC;
SELECT * FROM influencer_partnerships WHERE collaboration_type = 'sponsorship' ORDER BY collaboration_start_date DESC LIMIT 10;

SELECT id, influencer_name, partner_name, collaboration_type, collaboration_start_date, collaboration_end_date FROM influencer_partnerships WHERE influencer_name LIKE 'J%' OR partner_name LIKE 'A%' ORDER BY partner_name, collaboration_start_date;
SELECT influencer_name, COUNT(*) AS total_collaborations FROM influencer_partnerships GROUP BY influencer_name ORDER BY total_collaborations DESC;

SELECT influencer_name, partner_name, collaboration_type, DATEDIFF(collaboration_end_date, collaboration_start_date) AS collaboration_duration FROM influencer_partnerships WHERE collaboration_type IN ('sponsorship', 'affiliate') ORDER BY collaboration_duration DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT DISTINCT partner_name FROM influencer_partnerships ORDER BY partner_name DESC LIMIT 3;
SELECT * FROM influencer_partner WHERE partner_id = 1;
SELECT partnership_start_date, partnership_end_date, collaboration_description FROM influencer_partner WHERE influencer_id = 2;
SELECT partner_id, partnership_start_date, partnership_end_date FROM influencer_partner ORDER BY partnership_start_date DESC;
SELECT influencer_id, partnership_start_date FROM influencer_partner WHERE partnership_start_date < '2022-01-01';
SELECT * FROM collaboration_details WHERE collaboration_type = 'Sponsored Post' AND audience_reach > 10000 ORDER BY collaboration_date DESC;
SELECT partner_id, influencer_id, partnership_start_date FROM influencer_partner WHERE influencer_id = 1 ORDER BY partnership_start_date DESC;
SELECT influencer_id, COUNT(*) AS total_collaborations FROM collaboration_details GROUP BY influencer_id HAVING total_collaborations > 5;

SELECT partner_id, influencer_id, partnership_start_date, collaboration_description FROM influencer_partner INNER JOIN collaboration_details ON influencer_partner.partner_id = collaboration_details.partner_id;
SELECT influencer_id, partnership_start_date, partnership_end_date FROM influencer_partner WHERE partnership_end_date IS NULL;

SELECT partnership_start_date, partnership_end_date, collaboration_type FROM influencer_partner INNER JOIN collaboration_details ON influencer_partner.partner_id = collaboration_details.partner_id WHERE influencer_id = 2 ORDER BY partnership_start_date ASC;
SELECT * FROM Influencers;
SELECT influencer_name, category FROM Influencers WHERE follower_count > 1000;
SELECT partnership_id, partnership_type, partnership_date FROM Partnerships WHERE partnership_type = 'Sponsored';
SELECT collaboration_id, collaboration_details FROM Collaborations WHERE collaboration_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT influencer_name, follower_count FROM Influencers ORDER BY follower_count DESC;
SELECT * FROM Influencers ORDER BY influencer_name DESC;
SELECT influencer_name, follower_count FROM Influencers WHERE category='Fashion' AND follower_count > 10000;
SELECT partnership_type, partnership_date FROM Partnerships JOIN Influencers ON Partnerships.influencer_id = Influencers.influencer_id WHERE influencer_name LIKE '%J%' ORDER BY partnership_date DESC;
SELECT collaboration_details FROM Collaborations WHERE collaboration_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-12-31';
SELECT influencer_name, follower_count, partnership_type FROM Influencers JOIN Partnerships ON Influencers.influencer_id = Partnerships.influencer_id WHERE partner_id = 123;
SELECT * FROM Influencers;
SELECT influencer_name, followers_count FROM Influencers;
SELECT * FROM Brands WHERE industry = 'Fashion';
SELECT brand_name, category FROM Brands ORDER BY brand_name DESC;
SELECT collaboration_id, campaign_name FROM Collaborations WHERE collaboration_date >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT * FROM Influencers WHERE partnership_status = true;
SELECT influencer_name, followers_count FROM Influencers ORDER BY followers_count DESC;
SELECT * FROM Brands WHERE industry = 'Fashion' AND category = 'Apparel';
SELECT DISTINCT industry FROM Brands;
SELECT influencer_name, engagement_rate FROM Influencers INNER JOIN Metrics ON Influencers.influencer_id = Metrics.collaboration_id ORDER BY engagement_rate DESC;
SELECT * FROM influencers;
SELECT influencer_name, follower_count, category FROM influencers ORDER BY follower_count DESC;

SELECT * FROM partnerships WHERE payment_amount > 1000 ORDER BY payment_amount DESC;

SELECT influencer_name, category FROM influencers WHERE category = 'Fashion';
SELECT brand_name, industry FROM brands WHERE industry IN ('Tech', 'Fashion');
SELECT influencer_name, follower_count FROM influencers ORDER BY follower_count DESC;

SELECT brand_name, industry, COUNT(*) AS total_collaborations FROM brands JOIN partnerships ON brands.brand_id = partnerships.brand_id GROUP BY brand_name, industry ORDER BY total_collaborations DESC;
